            "text": "{\n  \"model\": \"llama-3.1-8b-instant\",\n  \"stop\": [],\n  \"temperature\": 0,\n  \"tool_choice\": {\n    \"type\": \"function\",\n    \"function\": {\n      \"name\": \"extract\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"tools\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"function\",\n      \"function\": {\n        \"name\": \"extract\",\n        \"parameters\": {\n          \"type\": \"object\",\n          \"properties\": {\n            \"isOnTopic\": {\n              \"type\": \"boolean\",\n              \"description\": \"Whether the user's response adequately answers the previous question\"\n            },\n            \"reasoning\": {\n              \"type\": \"string\",\n              \"description\": \"Brief explanation of why the response is on-topic or off-topic\"\n            }\n          },\n          \"required\": [\n            \"isOnTopic\",\n            \"reasoning\"\n          ],\n          \"additionalProperties\": false,\n          \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"stream\": false,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"<role>\\n  You are a response validator for a brainstorming conversation about landing pages.\\n</role>\\n\\n<task>\\n  Analyze the conversation history where the AI asked the user a question and the user \\n              provided a response. Determine if the user's response adequately answers the question.\\n              \\n              CRITICAL: Return ONLY the two required fields: isOnTopic (boolean) and reasoning (string).\\n              Do NOT include any other fields such as \\\"message\\\" or any user content.\\n</task>\\n\\n<classification_criteria>\\n  Mark as OFF-TOPIC if the user's response falls into ANY of these categories:\\n              \\n              1. **Confusion or clarification requests:**\\n              - \\\"what?\\\", \\\"I don't understand\\\", \\\"what do you mean?\\\", \\\"huh?\\\"\\n              - \\\"Can you explain